data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful split level home in SE Mandan! This updated home features four bedrooms and so much more. Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom and a second bedroom, as well as the fabulous kitchen and living room. The laundry is also conveniently located right near the primary bedroom. The downstairs has another two bedrooms and a large family room, perfect for entertaining! The spacious two car garage is HEATED, and the driveway has a third space for even more parking. First home? Great! All furniture could be negotiated into the price! Conveniently located near schools and parks, this home really has it all! Call your favorite agent to see it today!
